               <p>EDWIN HENRY THOMAS. I live at Birmingham. On the 2d of August I was in <placeName id="t18270913-254-crimeloc1430">Coventry-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18270913-254-crimeloc1430" type="placeName" value="Coventry-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18270913-254-crimeloc1430" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-254-off1428 t18270913-254-crimeloc1430"></join>, and heard a cry of Stop thief! from a gentleman who was with me; I felt my pocket, and my handkerchief was gone - I had had it a very few minutes before; I turned round and accused the prisoner of taking it - he denied it, but put his hands behind him, and dropped it on the pavement - I called the watchman, who took him.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
